WEBVTT

1
00:00:27.120 --> 00:00:28.399
I'm okay, you're okay?

2
00:00:28.399 --> 00:00:39.759
Hey, you put your arm around me.

3
00:00:39.759 --> 00:00:41.200
I know you said we shouldn't see each other,

4
00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:48.820
but I'm glad I was here to help.

5
00:00:48.820 --> 00:00:51.649
And is this from your family?

6
00:00:51.649 --> 00:00:56.460
Did you guys fight?

7
00:00:56.460 --> 00:00:57.740
I'm such a mess.

8
00:00:59.060 --> 00:01:01.060
My brother needs bail money,

9
00:01:01.060 --> 00:01:02.700
and my sister needs her tuition,

10
00:01:02.700 --> 00:01:06.420
and I just don't know what else to do.

11
00:01:06.420 --> 00:01:08.379
Hey, hey, hey.

12
00:01:08.379 --> 00:01:14.140
It's okay, I'm here to help.

13
00:01:14.140 --> 00:01:16.980
Listen, why don't you come stay in my place tonight?

14
00:01:16.980 --> 00:01:20.400
What you need is to rest peacefully.

15
00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:24.000
We should have taken care of you.

16
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:25.000
Yeah, sure.

17
00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:26.000
Yeah.

